WEBVTT

00:03.805 --> 00:06.660
A basketball icon is dead tonight.

00:06.981 --> 00:09.015
Mourned not just by the sports world...

00:09.122 --> 00:12.818
...but by anyone who valued relentless drive and achievement,...

00:13.359 --> 00:14.205
...Kobe Bryant.

00:17.151 --> 00:19.980
The man who could score 81 points in a single game,...

00:23.301 --> 00:26.315
...an all-star, an NBA champion for the Lakers,...

00:26.665 --> 00:28.579
...he was nicknamed the Black Mamba.

00:28.925 --> 00:32.281
But off the court, he was a devoted father of four girls,...

00:32.617 --> 00:34.549
...a husband of 18 years.

00:36.425 --> 00:40.323
He and his 13-year-old daughter Gianna were killed in a helicopter...

00:40.526 --> 00:42.581
...on their way to a basketball game.

